hadiths[47]{hadithnumber,text}:
349,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath nikley. hum sirf Haj hi ki niyat rakhtey they. jab hum sarf maqam mein pahunchey to mujhey haiz shuru ho gaya. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas aaye to main ro rahi thi. aap ney farmaya : tumhein kya huwa? haiz shuru ho gaya? mainey kaha : ji haan ! aap ney farmaya : ye aisi chiz hai jo Allah Taala ney Hazrat Adam alehissalam ki betiyon par likh di hai. tum wohi karo jo haji karen magar tawaf na karna."
350,"Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) jo ke Quraish ki shaakh banu-Asad sey talluq rakhti thin, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayen aur bataya ke us ( Fatima ) ko istihazey ka khoon aata hai. wo kehti hain ke aap ney farmaya : ye to eik rag ka khoon hai. jab haiz ka khoon aaney lagey to namaz chhod do aur jab khatam ho jaey to apney ( jism ) sey khoon dho lo aur naha kar namaz padh liya karo."
351,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab haiz ka khoon aaney lagey to namaz chhod do aur jab ruk jaey to ghusl karo."
352,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : Umme-Habiba bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! tehqiq mujhey istihazey ka khoon aata hai, to aap ney farmaya : ye eik rag hai, lihaza haiz khatam honey key baad ghusl kar key namaz padha karo. to wo har namaz key liye ghusl kya karti thin."
353,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo farmati hain ke Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey istihazey key khoon key barey mein puchha. aur Hazrat Aaisha bayan karti hain ke mainey unka tab khoon aalud pani sey bhara dekha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : jitney din tumhein pehley haiz aaya karta tha itney din namaz waghera sey ruk jao, phir ghusl kar key namaz padho. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : ) hamen Quteba ney dobara ye hadees bayan ki to ( Yazid bin abi Habib aur Irak bin Malik key darmiyan ) Jafar bin Rabeea ka zikr nahin kya."
354,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, farmati hain ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : tehqiq mujhey khoon aata rehta hai, isliye mein kabhi pak nahin hoti, to kya main mustaqil namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin, balke tum sirf itney din raat namaz chhodo jin dino mein tumhein haiz aaya karta tha, phir ghusl kar key langot baandh lo aur namaz shuru kar do."
355,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein bahut khoon aata tha. to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney uskey barey mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha to aap ney farmaya : bimari lagney sey pehley us ko jin shab o roz mein har maah haiz aaya karta tha, unka hisab lagaey aur har mahiney un dino mein namaz chhod dey. aur jab wo din guzar jaeyn to wo ghusl kerey. langot baandhey, phir namaz shuru kar dey."
356,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Umme-Habiba bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha), jo Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thin, in ko istihazey ka khoon aata rehta tha. wo pak nahin hoti thin. unka masla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney zikr kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye haiz nahin balke ye to reham mein koi zakham hai. wo apney dino ko yad karey jin mein usey haiz aaya karta tha, chunanche un dino mein namaz chhod dey, phir uskey baad wo har namaz key liye ghusl kya kerey."
357,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Umme-Habiba bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko saat saal istihaza raha, chunanche unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye haiz nahin balke ye to rag ka khoon hai. aap ney unhein hukm diya ke wo apney guzishta haiz key mutabiq namaz chhod den, phir ghusl kar key namaz shuru kar den. to wo har namaz key liye ghusl kar liya karti thin."
358,"Hazrat Fatima bint abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayen aur (be qaeyda ) khoon ki shikayat ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : ye eik rag ka khoon hai. tum hisab laga lo. jab tumharey haiz key din ayen to namaz na padho aur jab haiz key din guzar jaeyn to ghusl kar key agley haiz key aaney tak namaz padho. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain is hadees ko Hazrat Urwa sey Hisham bin Urwa ney bhi bayan kya hai, magar wo alfaz zikr nahin kiye jo munzir bin Mughira ney zikr kiye hain."
359,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Fatima bint abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayen aur kaha : tehqiq mujhey istihaza aata hai aur main pak nahin hoti, to kya main namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye to eik rag ka khoon hai. ye haiz nahin. jab haiz ka khoon aaye to namaz chhod do aur jab khatam ho jaey to khoon dho kar namaz padho."
360,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein istihaza aata tha. usey kaha gaya : tehqiq ye eik sarkash rag ka khoon hai. aur usey hukm diya gaya ke wo Zohar ko muakhkhar karey aur Asr ko jaldi karey aur dono key liye eik ghusl kerey. isi tarah maghrib ko muakhkhar karey aur Isha ko jaldi karey aur dono key liye eik ghusl kerey. aur subh ki namaz key liye alag ghusl kerey.
361,"Hazrat Zainab bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : tehqiq mein istihaza wali aurat hun. aap ney farmaya : apney haiz key dino mein namaz sey ruki raho, phir ghusl karo aur Zohar ko muakhkhar karo aur Asr ko jaldi karo aur ghusl kar key dono namazein padho. isi tarah maghrib ko muakhkhar karo aur Isha ko jaldi karo aur ghusl kar key dono namazein ikhatti padho. aur Fajr key liye alag ghusl karo."
362,"Hazrat Fatima bint abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke unhein istihaza aata tha. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : jab haiz ka khoon aaye, aur ye siyah khoon hota hai aur pehchana jata hai, to namaz sey ruk jaao. aur jab doosra khoon ho to wuzu kar key namaz padhti raho kyonkey ye eik rag ka khoon hai. Muhammad bin Musanna ney farmaya : ibne-abi Adi ney ye hadees hamen apni kitab sey bayan farmaai ( jab ke aainda hadees : 363 apney hafizey sey bayan farmaai)"
363,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Fatima bint abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza aata tha. to un sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq haiz ka khoon siyah hota hai aur pehchana jata hai. jab ye khoon ho to namaz sey ruk jaao. aur jab doosra khoon ( istihaza ) ho to wuzu kar key namaz padho. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees bahut sey raawiyon ney bayan ki hai lekin kisi ney wo lafz bayan nahin kiye jo ibne-abi Adi ney zikr kiye hain.
364,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Fatima bint abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza aata tha. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey istihaza (be qaeyda khoon) aata hai aur main kabhi pak nahin hoti, to kya namaz chhod dun? Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to eik rag ka khoon hai, haiz nahin. jab haiz aaney lagey to namaz chhod do. aur jab ruk jaey to khoon dho kar wuzu karo aur namaz padho kyonkey ye eik rag ka khoon hai, haiz nahin hai. raawi ney sey kaha gaya : kya haiz key ikhtitaam par wo ghusl keregi ? unhoney kaha : is main to kisi ko shak hi nahin. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke us hadees ko Hisham bin Urwa sey bahut sey raawiyon ney bayan kya hai magar Hammad key siwa kisi ney ( توضئی ) key lafz zikr nahin kiye. « wallah أعلم » ."
365,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Fatima bint abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayen aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey istihazey ka khoon aata hai aur main khoon sey pak nahin hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to eik rag hai, haiz nahin. jab haiz aaney lagey to namaz sey ruk jaao aur jab haiz khatam ho jaey to khoon dho kar namaz padho."
366,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Fatima bint abi Habish ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha ke main kabhi khoon sey pak nahin hoti to kya main namaz chhod dun? to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to eik rag ka khoon hai, haiz nahin. jab haiz aaney lagey to namaz chhod do aur jab haiz key din guzar jaeyn to khoon dho kar namaz padho."
367,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Fatima bint abi Habish ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main pak nahin hoti to kya namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye to eik rag hai, haiz nahin. jab haiz shuru ho to namaz chhod do aur jab khatam ho jaey to khoon dho kar namaz padho."
368,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum zard aur matyaley pani ko kuch nahin samajhti thin. ( haiz shumar nahin karti thin.)
369,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke yahudiyon mein jab kisi aurat ko haiz aata to wo uskey sath khatey peetey na unkey sath gharon mein rehtey. logon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaar di : ( ویسئلونک an المحیض قل ھواذی … … … ) aur log aap sey haiz key barey mein poochhtey hain. keh dijiye : wo paleed chiz hai, lihaza haiz ki haalat mein aurton ( key sath jima ) sey door raho. to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke unkey sath khaeyn-piyen aur gharon mein unhein sath rakhen aur jima key siwa sab kuch karen. Yahudi kehney lagey : ye Rasul to har chiz mein hamari mukhalifat karta hai. Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer aur Ibad bin Bishr (Raziallahu anha) khadey huye, aap ko ye baat batai aur kehney lagey : kya hum haiz ki haalat mein jima bhi kar liya keren? Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra sakht mutghaiyar ho gaya, yahan tak ke hamney samjha ke aap naraz ho gaey hain, lihaza wo uth khadey huye. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas doodh ka tohfa aa gaya to aap ney unkey peechey aadmi bheja, wo in ko wapis laya aur aap ney in ko doodh pilaya jis sey pata chal gaya ke aap un par naraz nahin hain."
370,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us shakhs key barey mein riwayat bayan kartey hain jo haiz ki haalat mein apni biwi sey jima karta hai ke wo eik deenar ya nisf deenar sadqa kerey.
371,Hazrat Umme-Salma Raziallahu anhuma farmati hain ke eik dafa mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath leti hui thi ke mujhey haiz shuru ho gaya. main aahista sey nikal gaee aur apney haiz key kapdey pehan liye. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tujhey haiz aa gaya? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney mujhey bulaya to main aap key sath chadar mein let gaee. us hadees key alfaz Ubedullah bin Saeed key hain.
372,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko eik chadar mein sotey they, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi. agar aap ko mujh sey kuch ( khoon waghera ) lag jata to aap us jagah ko dho letey, us sey zayed na dhotey, phir is mein namaz padh letey."
373,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab hum ( azwaje-mutahrat ) main sey koi haiz wali haalat mein hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey hukm detey ke wo apna izaar baandh ley, phir aap uskey sath let jatey."
374,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum ( azwaje-mutahrat ) main sey kisi ko haiz aaney lagta to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey hukm detey ke wo izaar baandh ley, phir aap uskey sath let jatey."
375,"Hazrat Jamee bin Umer ney kaha ke main apni walida aur khaala key sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya. hamney un sey puchha ke jab azwaje-mutahrat mein sey kisi ko haiz aaney lagta to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : jab hum mein sey kisi ko haiz aaney lagta, to aap usey hukm detey ke eik wasee izaar baandhey, phir us ka Sina aur pistaan apney jism sey laga letey."
376,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni biwiyon mein sey kisi biwi key sath let jaya kartey they jab ke usey haiz aa raha hota tha aur is par aadhi raanon tak ya ghutnon tak kapda hota. Les ki hadees mein hai ke wo us kapdey sey apney jism ko dhaanpey hoti thi.
377,"Hazrat Shureh sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : kya aurat haiz ki haalat mein apney khawind key sath kha sakti hai? unhoney farmaya : han, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey bulatey, mein haiz ki haalat mein aap key sath khati. aap eik ( gosht wali ) haddi pakadtey, phir mujhey qism detey, main us sey kuch gosht nochti, phir usey rakh deti to aap utha letey aur usey nochna shuru kar detey aur apna munh mubarak wahin rakhtey jahan mainey rakha tha. isi tarah pani mangwatey aur peeney sey pehley mujhey qism detey (ke main pehley piyun) mein pakadti aur kuch pani peeti, phir main rakh deti to aap utha letey aur us sey peetey aur apna munh mubarak wahin rakhtey jahan mainey rakha tha."
378,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apna munh mubarak us jagah rakhtey jahan sey mainey piya tha aur merey bachey huye pani sey peetey they, halanke main haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
379,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey bartan pakdatey, main us sey pani peeti thi jab ke main haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi, phir main bartan aap ko dey deti to aap merey munh ki jagah ka qasd (irada) kartey aur is par apna munh rakhtey."
380,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main haiz ki haalat mein piyaley sey pani peeti, phir main piyala Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pakda deti to aap apna munh merey munh ki jagah par rakh kar pani peetey. isi tarah mein koi haddi nochti jab ke main haiz ki haalat mein hoti, phir main wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pakda deti, to aap apna munh mubarak merey munh wali jagah par rakhtey."
381,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka sar mubarak hum (azwaje-mutahrat) mein sey kisi ki god mein hota tha jab ke wo haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi aur aap Quran padhtey they.
382,Hazrat Muaza Adwiya sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke haiz wali aurat haiz key dino ki namaz ki qaza ada karey ? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : kya to khaariji aurat hai? hamen Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein haiz aata tha. hum to namaz ki qaza ada nahin karti thin aur na hamen qaza ki adaegi ka hukm diya jata tha.
383,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein they ke aap ney farmaya : Aaisha! mujhey kapda pakdao. unhoney kaha : main in dino namaz nahin padhti. aap ney farmaya : wo ( tera haiz ) terey haath main to nahin. chunanche unhoney kapda pakda diya.
384,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey masjid sey chataai pakdao. mainey kaha : mujhey haiz aa raha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara haiz tumharey haath mein nahin hai. Is-haq bin Ibrahim ney kaha : hamen ye hadees abu-Muaawia ney bhi Aamash ki sanad sey isi tarah bayan ki hai.
385,"ummul-Mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apna sar mubarak hum mein sey kisi ki god mein rakh kar Quran Majeed tilawat farmatey halanke wo haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi. isi tarah hum mein sey koi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki chatai ley ja kar masjid mein bichhati thi, halanke wo haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
386,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo haiz ki haalat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar ko kanghi kar diya karti thin jab ke aap eetikaf mein hotey they. aap unhein apna sar pakda detey they aur wo apney hujrey hi mein hoti thin.
387,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : aap aetikaf ki haalat mein apna sar merey qarib farma detey they, mein us ko dho daalti thi, halanke mein haiz sey hoti thi."
388,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf ki haalat mein apna sar mubarak masjid sey (hujrey mein) nikal detey they aur main bawajud haiz ki haalat key aap ka sar mubarak dho diya karti thi.
389,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar mubarak ko bawajud haiz ki haalat key kanghi kar diya karti thi.
390,"Hazrat Hafsa sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr kartin to zarur kehtin : mera baap aap par fidaa ho. mainey un sey kaha : kya aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey aisey farmatey suna hai? wo kehney lagin : han, mera baap aap par fidaa ho. aap ney farmaya : baligh, parda nasheen aur haiz wali aurten eid key liye niklen, wo us neki aur musalmanon ki dua mein shareek hon, albatta haiz wali aurten namaz ki jagah sey alag rahen."
391,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke Hazrat Safiya bint Hui (Raziallahu anha) ( ummul-Mominin ) ko haiz aaney laga hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya, ho sakta hai wo hamen wapsi sey rok ley ? ( phir aap ney puchha : ) kya us ney tumharey sath baitullah ka tawaf nahin kya ? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : kyon nahin, balke kya tha. aap ney farmaya : phir chalo niklo."
392,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey Hazrat Asma bint Umes (Raziallahu anha) ki hadees key barey mein riwayat hai, jab unhein Zul-Hulefa ( Madina walon key ehraam baandhney ki jagah ) main bacha paida huwa tha, ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : usey kaho ke wo ghusl karey aur ehram baandhey."
393,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Umme-Kaab (Raziallahu anha) ka janaza padha jo ke bachey ki paidaish key moqey par faut ho gaee thin. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) janazey key doran mein unkey darmiyan khadey huye."
394,Hazrat Asma bint abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey haiz key khoon key barey mein puchha jo kapdey ko lag jaey ? to aap ney farmaya is ko ( kisi chiz sey) khurch do aur pani dal kar nakhunon sey malo aur phir dho kar is mein namaz padh lo.
395,Hazrat Umme-Qais bint Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey haiz key khoon key barey mein puchha jo kapdey ko lag jaey ? to aap ney farmaya : usey kisi lakdi (ya haddi waghera ) sey khurch do aur pani aur beri key patton sey dho do.
